In the zone last Friday night at @theoceanac shooting @bush. It was a very hard night for me physically (and mentally) but I tried to power through so that I could feel semi normal and “alive” for a moment doing what I love. It’s been a very challenging 14 months as I’ve been struggling with extreme health issues that has turned my world upside down. Most days I wake up just to make it through the day. It has tested my strength and resilience. It has made me appreciate every good moment as they have been far in between. We all have things in our lives we struggle with, it’s so important to surround yourself with good positive people/energy and to keep powering through no matter how difficult things are. Keep pushing through to do things you love and keep your passion alive 📷 #nevergiveup 

Thank you @michael_sparks_keegan for this photo 🙏🏻

#photographer #passion #love #inthezone #canon #rockphotography #rockphotographer #mylife #mood #moments @cdyates11
